{"tid":1673191,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook突被「禁網」？iPhone用戶晚上無法瀏覽各大專頁","createTime":"2019-10-24T13:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T13:52:46.000Z","uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b165a0304a90d38e18493ba1f1ed31f5e47bddb4","tid":1673191,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:42:36.000Z","msg":"反送中運動持續，行會成員葉國謙早前曾指，政府現階段考慮任何方法「止暴制亂」，不排除未來會「禁網」，惹起市民擔憂。「禁網」疑慮未除，今晚就有iPhone用戶發現未能瀏覽Facebook App上的個人專頁，當點擊時，均會顯示「無可用數據」。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》嘗試登入特首林鄭月娥、黃之鋒、香港警察、民間人權陣線等專頁，均出現「無可用數據」，不能瀏覽內容。惟Android手機用戶則沒有受影響，可如常瀏覽，暫未知當中原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191024&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60191865\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191024%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60191865&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNvilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=9d0046f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191024%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60191865&h=c1cb729a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191024&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60191865</a>"},{"pid":"677f730b5f8ddafeaa39690ff1563ba13a48c63f","tid":1673191,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4S58Lb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4S58Lb.jpg&h=8e2349f1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"13aca82ecfe160e35d15e8006a584376f9ea90bf","tid":1673191,"uid":265553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"原來又係 iPhone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3fd3d1be1a231fec2715c867f146e0ac997fd9","tid":1673191,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:49:14.000Z","msg"